OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,FThe King's US state visit has "all
OL,7,Fappropriate security measures" in
OL,8,Fplace, Britain's ambassador to the US
OL,9,Fhas said following what the White
OL,10,FHouse has called an attempted
OL,11,Fassassination of President Donald
OL,12,FTrump.
OL,14,FSir Christopher Turner said UK and US
OL,15,Fsecurity teams had been planning the
OL,16,Ftrip for weeks before the incident at
OL,17,Fthe media dinner, with changes
OL,18,Fpossible "as we go".
OL,26,@nD@_OUoD@^O]zD@JOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
