OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777269939
OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,FBuckingham Palace confirmed the visit
OL,7,Fwould "proceed as planned" after
OL,8,Fdiscussions were held on both sides of
OL,9,Fthe Atlantic and advice taken from the
OL,10,FGovernment.
OL,12,FSir Christopher, who replaced Peter
OL,13,FMandelson following his sacking over
OL,14,Fnew revelations about his relationship
OL,15,Fwith sex offender Jeffrey Epstein,
OL,16,Fsaid: "The real point is that our
OL,17,Frespective security teams have been in
OL,18,Fclose touch for weeks.
OL,26,@oD@GOUoD@ZO]xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777269939
OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,F"And any operational changes we have
OL,7,Fto make, we can make them as we go,
OL,8,Fand we are all very confident that all
OL,9,Fappropriate security measures are in
OL,10,Fplace."
OL,12,FSecurity teams in the UK and US worked
OL,13,Fthrough the night assessing the state
OL,14,Fvisit after the president was
OL,15,Fendangered when shots were fired
OL,16,Foutside the White House
OL,17,FCorrespondents' Association dinner on
OL,18,FSaturday evening in Washington.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
