CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777269939
OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,FWhile minor adjustments will be made
OL,7,Fto one or two royal engagements during
OL,8,Fthe trip, the overall plan remains
OL,9,Funchanged.
OL,11,FThe King and Queen are understood to
OL,12,Fhave reached out privately to the
OL,13,Fpresident and his wife, Melania, to
OL,14,Fexpress their sympathies with all
OL,15,Fthose affected on the night, and their
OL,16,Fgratitude to the security services who
OL,17,Fprevented further injury.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
