PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777269939
OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,FCharles and Camilla will arrive in
OL,7,FWashington on Monday for a four-day
OL,8,Fvisit aimed at marking the 250th
OL,9,Fanniversary of American independence
OL,10,Fand strengthening the special UK-US
OL,11,Frelationship, which has been under
OL,12,Fserious strain in recent months.
OL,14,FThe visit is the most important
OL,15,Fforeign trip of the King's reign so
OL,16,Ffar but now has the added element of
OL,17,Fincreased security concerns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777269939
OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,FIt comes at a pivotal moment for the
OL,7,FUK and US, with relations between
OL,8,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer and
OL,9,Fthe American leader fractious.
OL,11,FMr Trump has branded the UK's approach
OL,12,Fto the Iran war "terrible" and
OL,13,Frepeatedly lashed out at Sir Keir ` at
OL,14,Fone point describing him as "not
OL,15,FWinston Churchill".
OL,17,FReports have suggested the US could
OL,18,Freview its position on the Falkland
OL,19,FIslands in retaliation for Sir Keir's
OL,20,Flack of support for the war in Iran.
OL,26,@tD@QOUtD@ZO]vD@]OUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777269939
OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,FThe monarchy's soft power diplomacy is
OL,7,Fits strongest weapon in support of the
OL,8,FUK's overseas interests. There will be
OL,9,Fhope in Downing Street that Charles
OL,10,Fand Camilla can help put the UK-US
OL,11,Frelationship on a firmer footing.
OL,13,FMr Trump appears to have an affinity
OL,14,Fwith the King, saying when asked by
OL,15,Fthe BBC if the visit could help repair
OL,16,Fstrained transatlantic relations:
OL,17,F"Absolutely. He's fantastic. He's a
OL,18,Ffantastic man. Absolutely the answer
OL,19,Fis yes."
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777269939
OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,FThe president and his top team are
OL,7,Fsaid to be excited by the visit, with
OL,8,FUK officials not expecting any
OL,9,Fcontroversy during the four-day trip.
OL,11,FThere have been repeated calls by US
OL,12,Fcongressman Ro Khanna and the family
OL,13,Fof Virginia Giuffre, a victim of
OL,14,Fconvicted paedophile Jeffrey Epstein,
OL,15,Ffor a meeting with the King and Queen,
OL,16,Fbut sources have previously said the
OL,17,Fcouple will not meet them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777269939
OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,FThe legal implications of Charles and
OL,7,FCamilla coming into contact with any
OL,8,Fsurvivors of Epstein, and the King's
OL,9,Fconstitutional position, make a
OL,10,Fmeeting impossible while there are
OL,11,Fongoing UK police investigations.
OL,13,FThe historic visit, the King's first
OL,14,Fvisit to the US as monarch, will
OL,15,Fherald the start of celebrations
OL,16,Fmarking the 250th anniversary of the
OL,17,Fsigning of the Declaration of
OL,18,FIndependence, which came after forces
OL,19,Fled by George Washington defeated
OL,20,FCharles' forebear King George III's
OL,21,Farmy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777269939
OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,FMrs Trump has led the preparations for
OL,7,Fthe state visit, and highlights
OL,8,Finclude Charles' address to both
OL,9,Fhouses of Congress and the royal
OL,10,Fcouple commemorating the 25th
OL,11,Fanniversary of the September 11
OL,12,Fterrorist attacks that brought down
OL,13,FNew York's Twin Towers.
OL,15,FThe US leader and his wife will meet
OL,16,Ftheir royal guests when they arrive at
OL,17,Fthe White House's south portico on
OL,18,FMonday and escort them to the state
OL,19,Ffloor for private tea in the green
OL,20,Froom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
