PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777269939
OL,3,C'All appropriate security measures' in
OL,4,Cplace for King's US visit ` ambassador
OL,6,FMrs Trump announced last week the
OL,7,Fexpansion of the White House's long-
OL,8,Frunning honey-making programme,
OL,9,Fincluding a new beehive shaped like
OL,10,Fthe president's official residence,
OL,11,Fand after tea the two couples will
OL,12,Fvisit the bee homes, nestled on the
OL,13,FSouth Lawn near the historic
OL,14,Fbuilding's kitchen garden.
OL,16,FLater the King and Queen will attend a
OL,17,Fgarden party featuring guests
OL,18,Frepresenting the connection between
OL,19,Fthe US and UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
